title.narrative: North West Pacific Renewable Energy: Engineer to Contract Services

description.narrative: This Activity will identify how New Zealand can most effectively contribute to achieving the energy priorities of Micronesian countries through providing technical assistance and support for renewable energy generation. The Activity will also oversee the construction of the three Northwest Pacific solar photo-voltaic plants and one in Nauru.
